NK031(ki)006:1: // rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi spyi don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK031(ki)006:2: khog don snang ba'i 'od zer zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK031(ki)006:3: so // gang zhig srid dang zhi ba lam gyi chos //
NK031(ki)006:4: snga phyi'i bya byed bral bar rang byung nyid //
NK031(ki)006:5: gdod nas lhun rdzogs ngang las mi g.yo ba //
NK031(ki)006:6: gang du'ang rag las med phyir gnyis med 'dud //
NK031(ki)006:7: thar dka' srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' ring la //
NK031(ki)006:8: dgag sgrub rtsol ba'i rba la g.yengs gyur pa //
NK031(ki)006:9: gang de mi spong rtsal med thabs mchog gis //
NK031(ki)006:10: kun sgrol stan pa'i rgyal po rin po che //
NK031(ki)006:11: smra ba'i seng ge gzhung gi don rab 'byed //
NK031(ki)006:12: legs rtogs rigs pa'i gsung gi dbyangs bskad pas //
NK031(ki)006:13: log rtog brgyud pa'i wa tshogs skrag byed pa'i //
NK031(ki)006:14: mi pham dge ba'i bshes gnyen nyi phug pa //
NK031(ki)006:15: bla ma'i zhabs rdul nyi ma 'bum bdal ba //
NK031(ki)006:16: bdag blo'i pad+mosa 'dud do gsal don gang //
NK031(ki)006:17: rgyud rgyal dgongs pa zab sgram dpag dka' ba'i //
NK031(ki)006:18: khog don gsol 'debs don du ci nus brtsams //
NK031(ki)006:19: de la lung thams cad kyi rgyal po man ngag thams cad rtsa ba /
NK031(ki)006:20: rgyud dang mdo sde kun gyi spyi 'grel /
NK031(ki)006:21: bstan pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK031(ki)006:22: theg pa thams cad kyi snying khu /
NK031(ki)006:24: lta ba thams cad kyi me long /
NK031(ki)006:25: rgyal ba thams cad kyi yum /
NK031(ki)006:26: chos ma lus pa kun gyi mdo /
NK031(ki)006:27: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel bar byed pa /
NK031(ki)006:28: ye shes chen po'i snang ba mched par byed pa /
NK031(ki)006:29: rnam par rtog pa'i dra ba 'dral bar byed pa /
NK031(ki)006:30: nyon mongs pa'i phreng thag gcod par byed pa /
NK031(ki)006:31: sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho 'grol bar byed pa /
NK031(ki)006:33: skal ldan thams cad 'bad med du grol bar byed pa'i mdo /
NK031(ki)006:35: yid bzhin gyi nor bu chen po che lta bu'i
NK031(ki)006:36: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud 'di
NK031(ki)006:37: la / mtshon bya don gyi kun byed rgyal po dang /
NK031(ki)006:38: mtshon byed tshig gi kun byed rgyal po'o //
NK031(ki)006:40: sems can rang rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi
NK031(ki)006:41: sems gnas lugs rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa mnyam
NK031(ki)006:42: pa nyid kyi phyogs ris las grol ba'i stong gsal
NK031(ki)006:44: da lta'i shes rig wa le khyug ge ba 'di nyid do //
NK031(ki)006:45: 'di nyid ye gdod ma nas rang la rang chas su sgrub tu gnas kyang /
NK031(ki)006:46: ngo ma shes kyi rtog pas sgribs 'khrul bas nga
NK031(ki)006:47: bdag tu bzung rigs drug sdug bsngal gyi snang ba
NK031(ki)006:48: gnyis 'dzin du 'khrul pa 'di la mtshon byed tshig
NK031(ki)006:49: gi kun byed rgyal po mdo lung brgyad cu rtsa
NK031(ki)006:50: bzhi pa'i bdag nyid can 'dis mtshon cing gtan la
NK031(ki)006:51: 'bebs par byed pa la spyi don gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:52: dang po don gyi khog dbub pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:53: bar du dkyus kyi sa bcad pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:54: tha ma tshig gi 'bru gzhom pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:55: dang po la gnyis te bstan pa spyi ltar khog dbug pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:56: rgyud 'di nyid kyi gnas tshul lo //
NK031(ki)006:58: bgrang ngo de yang gsum du 'dud de gnas lugs 'khrul lugs 'khrul ba zlog thabs so //
NK031(ki)006:59: de las dang po 'khor ba dang mya ngan las
NK031(ki)006:60: 'das pa'i chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems rang
NK031(ki)006:61: byung gi ye shes su sangs rgyas par bstan pa
NK031(ki)006:62: ni / 'di nyid kyi zhe gnyis pa las /
NK031(ki)006:63: de nas byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po des /
NK031(ki)006:64: chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems kho nar sangs rgyas pa 'di gsungs so //
NK031(ki)006:67: 'dod pa'i khams kyi rang byung ye shes yin //
NK031(ki)006:68: gzugs kyi khams kyang rang byung ye shes yin //
NK031(ki)006:69: gzugs med khams kyang rang byung ye shes yin //
NK031(ki)006:70: kun byed rgyal po nga yis byed pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:71: nga byas thams cad ye shes ngo bor bshad //
NK031(ki)006:74: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK031(ki)006:75: rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK031(ki)006:76: khams gsum sems can thams cad kun //
NK031(ki)006:77: rtsol dang sgrub pa ma byas par //
NK031(ki)006:78: ye nas sangs rgyas lung bstan pas //
NK031(ki)006:82: thams cad rang byung ye shes su //
NK031(ki)006:83: dbyer med ngang du ye sangs rgyas //
NK031(ki)006:84: de la dgag sgrub ci yang med //
NK031(ki)006:85: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs pas 'khor ba dang
NK031(ki)006:86: 'das pa lam gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad snang
NK031(ki)006:87: ba dang stong pa gnyis su med pa'i byang chub
NK031(ki)006:88: kyi sems rgyu rkyen la rag ma las shing sgrib
NK031(ki)006:89: g.yogs dang bral ba'i ngang du ye nas sangs rgyas
NK031(ki)006:90: pa'o // de yang rang gi ye shes de la /
NK031(ki)006:93: gang du dgos pa gang nges pa //
NK031(ki)006:94: ngo bo dmigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:96: gsang sngags kyi spyi thems chen po bzhi 'chad de /
NK031(ki)006:105: snang ba la skyon du lta 'di chos nyid dang
NK031(ki)006:106: sangs rgyas gzhan du tshol ba'i zhen pa khrol ba
NK031(ki)006:109: yin pa'i ngo bo snang ba 'di yin te //
NK031(ki)006:110: 'di min snyam pa'i rgyu 'bras theg chen las //
NK031(ki)006:111: spongs 'gegs sbyong ba byin rlabs sna tshogs kyis //
NK031(ki)006:112: rang sems chos nyid bya med de las gol //
NK031(ki)006:113: rang gam bzhag nas gzhan ma rgyang du tshol //
NK031(ki)006:114: bya med bde bor rtsol ba dang du len //
NK031(ki)006:115: tshi chad pa yi nang du de las med //
NK031(ki)006:117: gnyis pa don gnyer ba ni /
NK031(ki)006:118: cir snang rang byung ye shes rtogs pas chos nyid
NK031(ki)006:119: dang sangs rgyas gzhan du tshol ba'i rtsol ba las
NK031(ki)006:121: de yang bcu gsum pa las /
NK031(ki)006:122: dgos ni khams gsum sems can kun //
NK031(ki)006:123: rang sems de bzhin nyid de mthong gyur na //
NK031(ki)006:124: sangs rgyas tshig gi sa la mi gnas te //
NK031(ki)006:125: da lta nyid nas shin tu rnal 'byor thob //
NK031(ki)006:128: gnyis med ye shes chen po'o //
NK031(ki)006:130: kye sems dpa' chen po gcig la gnyis du ma 'byed cig /
NK031(ki)006:131: bde ba sdug bsngal byang chub gcig /
NK031(ki)006:132: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su gcig /
NK031(ki)006:134: kun gsal de la rtog med pas //
NK031(ki)006:135: de ni rang byung ye shes yin //
NK031(ki)006:137: rang gi shes rgyud la sbyar na tha mal gyi shes pa 'di nyid do //
NK031(ki)006:139: zhe sdang rang byung ye shes chen po dang zhes pa la sogs pas gsal lo //
NK031(ki)006:141: sems nyid la rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed cing 'gag pa med pa'am sgrib g.yog med pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:143: rang byung rgyu rkyen med par byung ba yin //
NK031(ki)006:144: ye shes 'gag pa med par gsal ba yin //
NK031(ki)006:147: kye ma byas gdod nas grub pa'i chos nyid la /
NK031(ki)006:148: rgyu dang rkyen med brtsal med snying po ni /
NK031(ki)006:149: ma sgribs kun la phyogs ris med gsal bas //
NK031(ki)006:150: rang byung ye shes zhes su bstan pa yin //
NK031(ki)006:152: bzhi pa dmigs bzung ba gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:154: dang po gtan tshigs kyi gtan la phab ste don gyi dmigs bzung ba ni /
NK031(ki)006:155: ye shes gsang ba ltar na /
NK031(ki)006:156: ngang rang bzhin bdag nyid chen po gsum gyis gtan
NK031(ki)006:157: la dbab ste ngang gi gtan tshigs kyis chos thams
NK031(ki)006:158: cad ngos bzung dang bral bar gsal ba /
NK031(ki)006:159: rang bzhin gyi he dus 'dzin med kyi rig pa de nyid cir yang snang ba /
NK031(ki)006:160: bdag nyid chen po'i he dus tha mi dad de
NK031(ki)006:161: gnyis med kyi rang byung ye shes su gtan la
NK031(ki)006:162: dbab pa'o // de yang de nyid las /
NK031(ki)006:163: ye shes gsang ba'i rang bzhin ni //
NK031(ki)006:164: he du gsum gyis shes par bya //
NK031(ki)006:165: ngang gi rig pa gsal ba la //
NK031(ki)006:166: rang bzhin rig pa cir yang snang //
NK031(ki)006:167: bdag nyid snang stong tha dad med //
NK031(ki)006:168: de yang skye ba med pa'i ngos nas 'khor ba
NK031(ki)006:169: lam du ngos shing bzung du med de chos thams
NK031(ki)006:170: cad 'di phyir na 'di yin nges bzung dang bral
NK031(ki)006:171: bar btag la dbal rang bzhin 'gag med kyi ngos
NK031(ki)006:172: nas 'khor ba lam dgu 'du rang snang ste skye
NK031(ki)006:173: med nyid thams cad du ma 'gag par rang snang
NK031(ki)006:174: bar dbab / bdag nyid chen po'i ngos nas de
NK031(ki)006:175: gnyis gnyis su med de rang ye nas sems nyid
NK031(ki)006:176: snang stong gnyis med gcig tu gtan la dbab cing
NK031(ki)006:177: bar dbab / dmigs bzung ngo // zhes so //
NK031(ki)006:178: 'di nyid ltar na byang chub sems kyi he dus skye 'gag dbyer med du gtan dbab ste /
NK031(ki)006:180: byang pa gzung du yod pa ma yin la //
NK031(ki)006:181: chub pa kun gyi snying pos snying por chub //
NK031(ki)006:182: sems ni rang byung ye shes kun tu sems //
NK031(ki)006:184: gnyis pa rnam grangs rnam par phye ste dmigs gzung ba ni gnyis /
NK031(ki)006:185: theg pa thun mong gi ye shes gzhan dbang du bstan pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:186: a ti thun mong min pa'i ye shes rang 'byung ye shes su bstan pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:188: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa ba rnams la rang rang
NK031(ki)006:189: gi gzhung gi ye shes re yod pa de yin
NK031(ki)006:190: te de dag yul shes bya chos kyi dbyings re
NK031(ki)006:191: la shes byed rig pa'i ye shes re dmigs nas
NK031(ki)006:192: skye bas rig byed kyi ye shes zhes bya ste
NK031(ki)006:194: 'khor gyi ston pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK031(ki)006:195: yul la rtog pa'i ye shes te //
NK031(ki)006:196: gang su yul la rtog byed pa //
NK031(ki)006:197: de ni rig byed ye shes yin //
NK031(ki)006:199: de bas de dag rang 'byung gi ye shes ma yin te /
NK031(ki)006:201: yul la rtog pa'i ye shes de //
NK031(ki)006:202: yul las byung bas rang byung min //
NK031(ki)006:203: yul med tsal na gsal mi byed //
NK031(ki)006:206: rang 'byung ye shes gcig las med pa la /
NK031(ki)006:207: nga las byung ba'i 'khor gyi ston pa yis //
NK031(ki)006:208: yul la brten nas ye shes mi btags pa //
NK031(ki)006:209: rnam pa grangs kyi ye shes byung ba ni //
NK031(ki)006:210: rnam pa btags pa'i ye shes gcig gis ni //
NK031(ki)006:211: yul gcig rang bzhin so sor snang ba la //
NK031(ki)006:212: yul can la ni yul gyis ming btags pa //
NK031(ki)006:213: de ni nges pa ma yin 'khrul pas btag /
NK031(ki)006:214: kun byed rang byung ye shes min //
NK031(ki)006:216: gnyis pa a ti thun mong ma yin pa'i rang 'byung ye shes su bstan pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:217: shes bya chos kyi dbyings la shes byed rig pa'i ye shes dmigs nas skyes pa ma yin te /
NK031(ki)006:218: ye nas yul shes dbyer med du gsal bas rang 'byung ye shes so //
NK031(ki)006:220: yul de ye nas ye shes yin pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:221: yul dang ye shes gnyis su ngas ma bstan //
NK031(ki)006:222: des na yul yang rang byung yin //
NK031(ki)006:224: gsum pa gol sgrib gdar sha gcad de dmigs bzung ba ni /
NK031(ki)006:225: de ltar theg pa thun mong gi ye shes de
NK031(ki)006:226: dag rang gi phyogs mthong la ji bzhin par bzung
NK031(ki)006:227: nas rang 'byung gi ye shes phyogs med lhun grub
NK031(ki)006:228: las gol zhing de ma mthong bas sgribs te /
NK031(ki)006:230: rang 'byung ye shes chos nyid yul gcig la //
NK031(ki)006:231: chos gzhan mthong nas ye shes de spong byed //
NK031(ki)006:232: rang 'byung ye shes de dang 'phrad mi 'gyur //
NK031(ki)006:233: spong 'gegs yul can dag la ming mi grags //
NK031(ki)006:236: kun gyi mnyam nyid yin pa la //
NK031(ki)006:237: phyogs su bltas pas grub pa med //
NK031(ki)006:238: ces pa la sogs pas gsal lo //
NK031(ki)006:239: de yang gol sgrib de dag rang gi blo'i steng
NK031(ki)006:240: du gdar sha bcad nas a ti rang 'byung ye
NK031(ki)006:241: shes gshis ji bzhin pa gcig tu dmigs 'dzin pa'o
NK031(ki)006:243: da lta'i bde dang phyi ma'i bde //
NK031(ki)006:244: mngon sum pa dang rgyab nas 'byung //
NK031(ki)006:245: de yang rnam pa'i skyon yin pas //
NK031(ki)006:246: de la brten par mi bya'o //
NK031(ki)006:249: kun byed rgyal pos 'khor la lung bstan pa //
NK031(ki)006:250: ye shes sgribs med gsal ba'i don du bstan //
NK031(ki)006:251: rang 'byung rgyu rkyen med pa'i snying por gnas //
NK031(ki)006:252: rtog pa sgro skur 'das pa'i dgongs pa yin //
NK031(ki)006:254: 'o na gshis de dbyer med la ye sangs rgyas par brjod pa ci zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:255: de ni dgos dgongs kyi brjod pa ste rgyu theg
NK031(ki)006:256: pa sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyur 'dod cing sangs
NK031(ki)006:257: rgyas gzhan du tshol ba'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i ched
NK031(ki)006:258: du / ngo bo la skyed bogs dbyung du med
NK031(ki)006:259: pa la dgongs nas ye sangs rgyas par bshad du
NK031(ki)006:260: du / zad kyis / gnas lugs sangs rgyas sems
NK031(ki)006:261: can sogs dbyer med cing gang gis phyogs su ltung
NK031(ki)006:262: du / zad kyis / ba med do // de
NK031(ki)006:263: ni rang bzhin gan sa lugs kyi rdzogs pa chen
NK031(ki)006:265: gzhi rdzogs pa chen po zhes kyang bya ste dngos po rnams kyi gnas lugs /
NK031(ki)006:266: shes bya rnams kyi gshis sam 'dug tshul lo //
NK031(ki)006:268: de ltar sangs rgyas kyang khams gsum gyi sems can
NK031(ki)006:269: rnams kyis rgyu mtshan gsum gyi sgo nas ma rtogs
NK031(ki)006:270: te 'khrul pa'i tshul bstan pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:272: gnyis med ngang du ye nas sangs rgyas kyang //
NK031(ki)006:273: las dang nyon mongs ma rig rgyu gnyis kyis //
NK031(ki)006:274: dus gsum rgyun du 'khrul ba'i spyod yul snang //
NK031(ki)006:277: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid mngon sum gnas
NK031(ki)006:278: pa la grib ma gzugs kyi dpe bzhin de la
NK031(ki)006:281: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas ye sangs rgyas
NK031(ki)006:282: pa yin pa la yin par ngo ma shes pa
NK031(ki)006:283: dang / kun tu rtags pa'i ma rig pas der ma zad phyin ci log tu brtags pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:284: yang dag pa'i lam dang bral bas ma rtogs de 'khrul pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:286: dper na 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po gcig la sras rgyal sa zin pa gcig yod pa la /
NK031(ki)006:287: yang rgyal bu gcig mthong bas /
NK031(ki)006:288: rgyal mi mched rje mi spun bya ba yin gsungs nas /
NK031(ki)006:289: rgyal bu de'i bla g.yas pa la btsad kyi me btsa' pan lta bu gcig btab kyang zer /
NK031(ki)006:290: yang na gser gyi g.yung drung ris gcig btab /
NK031(ki)006:291: phrag gong g.yas g.yon du nyi zla'i gzugs brnyan bkod
NK031(ki)006:292: nas nang blon pa glo ba nye ba gcig la
NK031(ki)006:293: bskur nas rgyal khams thag ring gcig tu sprugs pas
NK031(ki)006:294: dang po rang nyid rgyal bu yin pa la yin
NK031(ki)006:295: par ngo ma shes pa dang 'dra bar /
NK031(ki)006:296: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas ye sangs rgyas
NK031(ki)006:297: pa yin pa la yin par ngo ma shes pa
NK031(ki)006:299: rgyud drug gnas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis /
NK031(ki)006:300: rang gi rang bzhin rang gis ngo ma shes /
NK031(ki)006:303: byang chub de bzhin nyid du ma rig ste //
NK031(ki)006:304: ma rig rtog pa'i mun pa 'thibs pa la //
NK031(ki)006:306: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK031(ki)006:307: 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas //
NK031(ki)006:308: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas //
NK031(ki)006:309: kun nas slong ba'i sa bon byas //
NK031(ki)006:311: gnyis pa kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:312: dper na rgyal bu des ngo ma shes kyis mi
NK031(ki)006:313: mod de rang nyid dmangs ma yin pa la dmangs
NK031(ki)006:314: su sgro btags pa ltar lhan skyes kyis ngo ma
NK031(ki)006:315: shes kyis mi mod de kun tu brtags pa'i ma
NK031(ki)006:316: rigs pas rang rig la bdag tu sgro btags /
NK031(ki)006:317: rang snang la bdag dang bdag gi dang gzhan du
NK031(ki)006:318: sgro brtags te bdag las gzhan 'dra gcig las gnyis
NK031(ki)006:321: ma rig log rtog gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK031(ki)006:322: yul drug chos la nges brtags pas //
NK031(ki)006:323: 'jig pa drug dang rten pa drug /
NK031(ki)006:324: 'jig rten zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK031(ki)006:327: snang med bde chen rang snang las //
NK031(ki)006:328: brtag pa'i snang bas gnyis su mthong //
NK031(ki)006:331: las dang nyon mongs rkyen byas nas //
NK031(ki)006:332: kun brtags ma rig pa yis 'khor //
NK031(ki)006:334: gsum pa yang dag pa'i lam dang bral ba ni /
NK031(ki)006:335: dper na rgyal bu rkang 'khyams de la khyod rgyal
NK031(ki)006:336: po'i sras yin yab mes dang mnga' thang dang chab
NK031(ki)006:337: srid 'di yin no zhes lo rgyus skod mkhan med
NK031(ki)006:338: pas kyang ngo ma shes te rgyal bu dmangs su
NK031(ki)006:339: 'khyams pa ltar / ma rig pa gnyis kyis sgribs
NK031(ki)006:340: pa de la yang dag pa'i lam dang bral bas
NK031(ki)006:341: kyang ngo ma shes te 'khrul ba'o //
NK031(ki)006:342: de yang khu byug gi rgyud las /
NK031(ki)006:343: so so'i skye bos mi shes pa //
NK031(ki)006:344: shes pa gsum po spangs pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:345: sku gsum las ni ring du gyur //
NK031(ki)006:347: 'o na yang dag pa'i lam rang gang yin zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:348: gong ltar shes par gsum yin la /
NK031(ki)006:349: 'di nyid kyi gsum pa ltar na yang dag pa'i dug lnga la bzhag ste /
NK031(ki)006:351: sku gsum ston pa de'i 'khor rnams la //
NK031(ki)006:352: rnam par thar pa'i lam ni rnam lnga ste //
NK031(ki)006:353: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi lam du bstan //
NK031(ki)006:354: rang byung ye shes lnga yi lam lnga ni //
NK031(ki)006:355: 'dod chags dang ni zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK031(ki)006:356: nga rgyal dang ni phrag dog rnam lnga ste //
NK031(ki)006:357: rang byung ye shes rnam lnga kun gyi lam //
NK031(ki)006:359: de rang ji ltar zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:361: 'dod pa chos rnams bdag tu 'dod pa yin //
NK031(ki)006:362: chags pa bdag tu 'dod pa de la chags //
NK031(ki)006:363: zhe ba skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK031(ki)006:364: sdang ba cho 'phrul sna tshogs de la sdang //
NK031(ki)006:365: gti mug mi rtog pa yi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK031(ki)006:366: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la dbye bsal med //
NK031(ki)006:367: nga ni ma nor ba yi byang chub sems //
NK031(ki)006:368: de bzhin nyid du ye nas rgyal bar byed //
NK031(ki)006:369: thams cad de bzhin nyid du gcig pa la //
NK031(ki)006:370: yin min sgro skur 'debs la phrag dog byed //
NK031(ki)006:372: don chos nyid rtog pa dang 'du 'bral med pa'i yang dag pa'i 'dod chags /
NK031(ki)006:373: gnyis med rtog pas mtshan ma sna tshogs la sdang ba'i zhe sdang /
NK031(ki)006:374: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la gang yang dbye bsal med pa'i gti mug /
NK031(ki)006:375: de bzhin nyid rtog pa las gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'i nga rgyal /
NK031(ki)006:376: lta spyod dman pa 'di'i khog tu mi tshud pa'i
NK031(ki)006:377: phrag dog lnga po de yang dag pa'i lta snol
NK031(ki)006:378: yin pa dang bral nas phyi srid pa dang srid
NK031(ki)006:379: pa'i yo byad la tsha la dang gar spyin ltar
NK031(ki)006:380: lhag par zhen cing chags pa'i 'dod chags la sogs
NK031(ki)006:381: pa'i log pa'i dug lnga la spyad pas 'khor bar
NK031(ki)006:382: 'khyams pas sdug bsngal gyi nyam thag pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:384: dmyal ba la sogs 'gro ba ris drug gis //
NK031(ki)006:385: cha grang bkres skom glen lkugs ltung 'gyur rnams //
NK031(ki)006:388: rkam chags lnga yi rnam smin gyis //
NK031(ki)006:389: lam sgor lnga ru zhugs phyin nas //
NK031(ki)006:390: mi bde sdug bsngal lnga la spyod //
NK031(ki)006:392: gsum pa de ltar sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag pa
NK031(ki)006:393: de dag rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i thugs thams
NK031(ki)006:394: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gzigs pa'i tshul ni
NK031(ki)006:396: de nas bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po
NK031(ki)006:397: des 'khor rnams yongs su 'dun pa de gzigs nas
NK031(ki)006:400: gzigs pa'i rgyu mtshan dang gzigs pa'i tshul dang /
NK031(ki)006:404: rang rgyud dag pa'i rgyal ba thams cad kyi //
NK031(ki)006:405: de dang der ni dbyer med de nyid du //
NK031(ki)006:406: mngon byas phyir dang nyid las mi gzhan phyir //
NK031(ki)006:407: nyid kyi log rtog dag phyir thams cad mkhyen //
NK031(ki)006:409: ye shes kyi dbyings las mi gzhan pa'i don mngon du byas pa dngas /
NK031(ki)006:410: bdag nyid gcig pa'i las dang thugs rje'i 'brel ba
NK031(ki)006:411: yod pa dang nyid kyi log rtog rtsa ba nas
NK031(ki)006:413: de yang rgyud gzhan dag las /
NK031(ki)006:414: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK031(ki)006:415: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK031(ki)006:416: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK031(ki)006:417: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK031(ki)006:420: byang pa'i ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis cir yang ma dmigs par gzigs pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:421: chub pa'am ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis cir yang ma 'gag par gzigs pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:422: sems sam dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis thams cad dbyer med du gzigs pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:423: gsum pa brtsad pa spang ba ni gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:425: bye brag ji snyed pa'i ye shes kyi brtsad spang ngo //
NK031(ki)006:430: 'o na rgyal bas gdul bya gzigs pa de yul du byas nas gzigs sam /
NK031(ki)006:431: yul du ma byas par gzigs sam /
NK031(ki)006:432: yul yul can dbyer med du gzigs /
NK031(ki)006:435: yul dang yul can gnyis 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:436: dper na mig shes dang gzugs bzhin no //
NK031(ki)006:437: gnyis pa ltar na gzigs par mi rigs te yul
NK031(ki)006:438: du ma byas pa'i phyir dper na mig shes kyi
NK031(ki)006:439: sgra bzhin no // gsum pa ltar na /
NK031(ki)006:441: gzigs bya gzigs byed du ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK031(ki)006:442: dper na mig gis mig bzhin no zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:444: skad yangs par bkye ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:446: dang po ni yul du byas nas kyang gzigs /
NK031(ki)006:447: yul du ma byas par yang gzigs /
NK031(ki)006:448: yul yul can dbyer med du'ang gzigs zhes bya /
NK031(ki)006:450: chub pa'am ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK031(ki)006:451: ngos nas gzigs bya'i yul dang gzigs byed kyi mkhan
NK031(ki)006:452: po ltar yang ma 'gags par gzigs te /
NK031(ki)006:454: kun bzang ye shes mchog thugs la //
NK031(ki)006:455: snga ma 'gags la phyis mi sgrib //
NK031(ki)006:456: rnam pa'i khyad par dus bzhin du //
NK031(ki)006:457: ye shes so sor gsal khyad med //
NK031(ki)006:459: 'o na gzung 'dzin can du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:460: mi 'gyur te gzigs bya gzigs byed kyi snang ba
NK031(ki)006:461: ma 'gag la de gnyis kyis mthas ma reg par
NK031(ki)006:462: thugs su chud pa'i phyir ro //
NK031(ki)006:463: de yang spyi mdo'i zhe gnyis pa las /
NK031(ki)006:464: lang ka'i bdag po gang dam pa rnams de kho
NK031(ki)006:465: na nyid las ma g.yos par sems can gyi khams
NK031(ki)006:466: 'du shes mtha' thugs pa med pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:467: sgra dang gzungs dang spyod pa mtha' thugs pa med pa rnams mi mkhyen pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:470: mi 'grel ba ni gang yang med do //
NK031(ki)006:472: chos sku skye med rig pa'i rgyud las /
NK031(ki)006:473: rnam par rtog med ye shes thugs //
NK031(ki)006:474: cir yang sa le thams cad mkhyen //
NK031(ki)006:477: bram ze mo dang mtshang can gyis //
NK031(ki)006:478: rngon pa'i g.yog po mthong ba la //
NK031(ki)006:479: re dang dogs pa'i sems 'byung ba //
NK031(ki)006:480: dpon gyis legs par mthong ba bzhin //
NK031(ki)006:481: de bzhin 'gro ba khyod kyis gzigs //
NK031(ki)006:482: zhes pa'i gtam rgyud kyang gsung ngo //
NK031(ki)006:483: yul du ma byas par yang gzigs te /
NK031(ki)006:484: byang pa'i ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK031(ki)006:485: ngos nas yul dang yul can ma dmigs la ma
NK031(ki)006:487: de yang bdun cu pa las /
NK031(ki)006:488: de nas byang chub sems dam kun byed rgyal po des /
NK031(ki)006:489: chos thams cad skye ba med par mnyam pa la
NK031(ki)006:490: gzigs shing dgongs nas ci yang mi gsung par bzhugs
NK031(ki)006:492: 'o na gzigs pa rang du mi rigs zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:493: yul med pa la med par gzigs pa mi 'gal te /
NK031(ki)006:494: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis kyang //
NK031(ki)006:495: ye shes yul med cang mi gzigs //
NK031(ki)006:498: yul yul can dbyer med du yang gzigs te /
NK031(ki)006:499: sems sam dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi ngos
NK031(ki)006:500: nas gzigs bya gzigs byed dbyer med du gzigs pa'o
NK031(ki)006:502: nyid las mi gzhan don nyid kyis //
NK031(ki)006:503: me long tshul du gzigs par 'gyur //
NK031(ki)006:505: 'o na gang gis gang gzigs te gzigs pa rang gi sgra mi 'jug go zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:506: gshis la yul shes la sogs pa chos thams cad
NK031(ki)006:507: dbyer med yin pa la yin pa bzhin du gzigs
NK031(ki)006:508: pa ni shin tu yang gzigs pa'i mchog yin pas
NK031(ki)006:509: sgra 'jug ste / nyer drug pa las /
NK031(ki)006:510: mngon sum mthong bas mthong med mngon sum mthong ba'i mig /
NK031(ki)006:511: de phyir thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan zhes kyang ni de la bya /
NK031(ki)006:513: gnyis pa skad dog par bkyer na /
NK031(ki)006:514: yul du byas nas gzigs zhes sgro mi 'dogs /
NK031(ki)006:515: yul du ma byas zhes skur pa mi 'debs te
NK031(ki)006:516: yul yul can gyi tha snyad las grol te dbyer
NK031(ki)006:517: med par gzigs pa kho na'o //
NK031(ki)006:518: de yang gong du bshad pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:520: chos sku ston pa kun bzang ngas //
NK031(ki)006:521: ma lus ye shes chen por mkhyen //
NK031(ki)006:523: gnyis pa bye brag ji snyed pa'i brtsad spang ni /
NK031(ki)006:525: sangs rgyas kyis ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal la
NK031(ki)006:526: sogs pa mkhyen cing gzigs pa de nyams su myong
NK031(ki)006:527: nas mkhyen nam ma myong nas yang mkhyen /
NK031(ki)006:528: dang po ltar na rtog bcas su thal ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:529: gnyis pa ltar na mi rung ste /
NK031(ki)006:530: sngar ma zos pa'i zas kyi ro mi shes pa bzhin no zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:532: kha cig dag 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sangs rgyas kyi
NK031(ki)006:533: nyams su ma myong yang mkhyen du btub ste dper
NK031(ki)006:534: na sman pa mkhas pas lus kyi rtsa chu la
NK031(ki)006:535: brten nas nad ji ltar gnas pa ltar shes la
NK031(ki)006:536: / de ltar shes kyang sman pas nad sdug bsngal
NK031(ki)006:537: nyams su myong mi dgos pa bzhin no zhes 'go
NK031(ki)006:539: 'di la ru shangs pa'i zhal nas de ltar na
NK031(ki)006:540: rjes dpag gis spyi rnams las mi mkhyen par thal
NK031(ki)006:541: lo // des na brtsad pa dang spang ba gnyis ka 'khrul ba'i rnam bzhag yin te /
NK031(ki)006:542: nyams su myong ma myong ba'i tha snyad de zag
NK031(ki)006:543: bcas tshogs sbyor ba man chad la btsi ba yin
NK031(ki)006:544: gyis / zag med mthong sgom man chad na chos
NK031(ki)006:545: nyid mngon sum du gyur pa'i phyir nyams su myong
NK031(ki)006:546: ma myong gi rtsod pa dang bral bas sangs rgyas
NK031(ki)006:547: la lta mi smos pas rang rig gis khrel ba'i
NK031(ki)006:550: rtog med du gzigs pa yin pas de la nyams
NK031(ki)006:551: su myong ma myong gi rtsis gdab dang tha snyad
NK031(ki)006:552: las 'das pa'i tshul gyis mkhyen cing gzigs te dper
NK031(ki)006:553: na drang srong mngon shes can gyis drung gi rmi
NK031(ki)006:554: lam gyi sdug bsngal gyis gdung ba'i sems rgyud shes
NK031(ki)006:555: pa bzhin no // de yang dkon brtsegs las /
NK031(ki)006:556: ji ltar bu mo'i rmi lam na //
NK031(ki)006:557: bu gcig byung ba shi 'phos na //
NK031(ki)006:558: dga' dang sdug bsngal tshogs byung ba //
NK031(ki)006:559: de bzhin 'gro ba khyod kyis gzigs //
NK031(ki)006:561: de ni gong ma'i la skyon bkal ba zad mod
NK031(ki)006:562: kyi rang lugs dbu mar gol ba ma tshogs par
NK031(ki)006:563: 'dug bsam ste bla ma'i gsung yin pas brtags la
NK031(ki)006:565: spyir na sangs rgyas kyi ye shes thams cad ji
NK031(ki)006:566: lta ba dang ji snyed pa gnyis su 'dus so
NK031(ki)006:568: shes bya'i gshis ji lta bar mkhyen pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:569: gshis la gzigs bya'i yul sems can dang gzigs byed
NK031(ki)006:570: kyi mkhan po rgyal ba gnyis su med pa yin
NK031(ki)006:571: la de ka rgyal bas mkhyen pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:573: gnas lugs la de ltar yin mod kyang sems can
NK031(ki)006:574: rnams kyis de ltar ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis sdug
NK031(ki)006:575: bsngal gyis nyam thag pa de gzigs pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:576: de bas na de la thugs rje yang skye ba'o gsung skad de /
NK031(ki)006:577: spyir gsang sngags de las kyang rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK031(ki)006:578: gzhung gis rang 'byung gi ye shes gcig la yon
NK031(ki)006:579: tan gyi cha nas ming gi tha snyad ji ltar
NK031(ki)006:580: btags kyang thams cad dbyer med du mkhyen cing dbyer
NK031(ki)006:581: med du gzigs pa kho na las spros pa gzhan
NK031(ki)006:583: spyi don bzhi pa gzigs nas thugs rje skye tshul bstan pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:585: nga ni thugs rje'i ngo bo ste /
NK031(ki)006:588: thugs rje ye shes kyi 'od zer bskul ba spros pas /
NK031(ki)006:594: dang po ni rgyu ni ston pa lhun grub kyi
NK031(ki)006:595: mdzad pa mi 'gog pa yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK031(ki)006:596: lta bu ste / ye shes gsang ba las /
NK031(ki)006:597: 'od gsal dbyings la bzhugs bzhin du //
NK031(ki)006:598: thugs rje'i mdzad pa phyogs bcur bdal //
NK031(ki)006:599: gdul bya'i bsam bzhin re ba skongs //
NK031(ki)006:600: yid bzhin nor bu lta bur snang //
NK031(ki)006:602: rkyen ni gdul bya las dag pa brgya byin dang 'jog po lta bu gsung ste /
NK031(ki)006:603: las ma dag pa la yang gang 'tshams su 'byung ste yod pa nyid kyis 'char ro //
NK031(ki)006:604: yang de nyid las 'gro ba gang gi ngo dag tu //
NK031(ki)006:606: skal ldan gdul bya mchis pa na //
NK031(ki)006:607: thugs rje gdul bya bzhin du 'byung //
NK031(ki)006:608: gdul bya gang yang mi gnas na //
NK031(ki)006:609: thugs rje'i mdzad pa gang la 'char //
NK031(ki)006:612: ngo bo gnyis med yin pa'i skye bya skye byed
NK031(ki)006:613: gnyis med kyang gdul bya'i ngo la skye ba ltar
NK031(ki)006:615: sangs rgyas sems can dbyer med gcig btab pas rtogs na /
NK031(ki)006:616: thugs rje chen po skye zhes de la bya //
NK031(ki)006:620: thugs rje chen po gdul bya la //
NK031(ki)006:621: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK031(ki)006:625: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs phrad gsol /
NK031(ki)006:629: dang po rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje skye ba chu bo chen po'i gzhung lta bu ni /
NK031(ki)006:630: ston pa kun byed rgyal pos dus gsum rgyun du
NK031(ki)006:631: skal ldan la 'bad med grol ba'i lung nges par
NK031(ki)006:632: ston pa ste / gya bzhi pa las /
NK031(ki)006:633: kun byed rgyal po 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' bas //
NK031(ki)006:634: snga bar gsungs shing phyi par gsung 'gyur la //
NK031(ki)006:635: da ltar byung bar gsung pas skal ldan la //
NK031(ki)006:636: nges par bstan pas 'bad med grol ba'i lung //
NK031(ki)006:638: 'di la skye sa dang skye mkhan gnyis su gsung
NK031(ki)006:639: yang sems can rnams kyi sems nyid rang 'byung ye
NK031(ki)006:640: shes dus gsum du 'pho 'gyur med pa de nyid
NK031(ki)006:641: pas de la gnyis su dbyer med bsam /
NK031(ki)006:642: gnyis pa rang bzhin shugs kyi skye ba'i thugs rje nyi ma'i 'od lta bu ni /
NK031(ki)006:643: kun byed rgyal po'i rang bzhin las ma brtsal bar
NK031(ki)006:644: lhun gyi grub pa'i sku gsum gyi thugs rje rtsol
NK031(ki)006:645: ba med par shugs la skye ba ste /
NK031(ki)006:647: kun byed byang chub nga yi rang bzhin las //
NK031(ki)006:648: ma brtsal rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa yi //
NK031(ki)006:649: rgyal ba kun gyi snying po sku gsum ste //
NK031(ki)006:652: sku gsum rig pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK031(ki)006:653: thugs rje nyi ma'i zer shar nas //
NK031(ki)006:655: thabs kyi rig pa rang shar nas //
NK031(ki)006:656: ye shes gsal bas 'gro don mdzad //
NK031(ki)006:657: ye shes rang bzhin 'dren skur shar //
NK031(ki)006:659: gsum pa yul dang phrad pa'i thugs rje skye ba
NK031(ki)006:660: yul sdug bsngal phung po dang 'phrad pas snying rje
NK031(ki)006:663: ma rig rnams la snying rje yongs kyi skye //
NK031(ki)006:665: spyir kun la skye yang khyad par du a ti
NK031(ki)006:666: yo ga'i lam 'di spong zhing lam gzhan ma nor
NK031(ki)006:667: ba yin no zhes ston cing spyod pa de la
NK031(ki)006:670: lam 'di spong zhing mtha' dang lam gzhan lam du bltas nas ma nor lam zhes ston pa de /
NK031(ki)006:671: de dag rdo la gser bzhin thugs rje rang byung
NK031(ki)006:672: zhing thugs rje'i shugs kyi kye ma 'phrogs pa yin
NK031(ki)006:674: bzhi pa skul zhing gsol ba btab pas skye ba'i
NK031(ki)006:675: thugs rje sdug phongs kyis phos pas snying rje skye
NK031(ki)006:676: ba lta bu ni gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:677: rang don du gsol ba btab pas skyes pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:678: gzhan don du gsol ba btab pas skyes pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:680: don gyi phyogs gcig dper bya na /
NK031(ki)006:681: yi dam lha la mchod pa phul bzlas brjod byas
NK031(ki)006:682: nas gsol ba btab pas 'khor ba'i du kha las
NK031(ki)006:683: grol zhing dngos grub thob pa lta bu'o //
NK031(ki)006:684: gnyis pa ni rang don du zhu mi dgos kyang
NK031(ki)006:685: gzhan don du gsol ba btab pas thugs rje skyes
NK031(ki)006:686: pa ste sngon 'byung sum cu rtsa gsum du lha'i
NK031(ki)006:687: bu sems lhag can gyi don du sprul pa'i brgya
NK031(ki)006:688: byin gyis phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams la bskul ba
NK031(ki)006:689: / gsung gi mnga' bdag thams cad kyis /
NK031(ki)006:690: rtsol ba'i theg pa mthar bton na /
NK031(ki)006:691: rtsol med theg pa mi gsung pa //
NK031(ki)006:692: thugs rje chen po yal lam ci //
NK031(ki)006:693: skal ldan gdul bya mchis pa na //
NK031(ki)006:694: lhun grub theg pa gsung du gsol //
NK031(ki)006:695: zhes gsol ba btab pa las phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams kyis sems dpa' rdo rje la /
NK031(ki)006:696: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK031(ki)006:697: sku'i rang bzhin khyod yin pas //
NK031(ki)006:698: rmad byung rol pa'i sku ru shar //
NK031(ki)006:699: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad kyi //
NK031(ki)006:700: gsung gi bdag nyid rig pa'i gsung //
NK031(ki)006:701: rmad byung rol pa'i gsung du shar //
NK031(ki)006:702: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad kyi //
NK031(ki)006:703: thugs kyi rang bzhin khyod yin pas //
NK031(ki)006:704: sangs rgyas kun gyi mdzad pa shar //
NK031(ki)006:705: gsung gi mnga' bdag thams cad kyi //
NK031(ki)006:706: ye shes rang bzhin khyod yin pas //
NK031(ki)006:707: thams cad byang chub sems su gsal //
NK031(ki)006:708: tshig gcig don kun rdzogs pa'i bdag /
NK031(ki)006:709: rin chen 'phrul gyi snying po'i sgo //
NK031(ki)006:710: skal ldan rnams la bstan du gsol //
NK031(ki)006:711: rin chen 'phrul gyi thabs ldan pas //
NK031(ki)006:712: gang 'dod mthun pa'i sgo de nas //
NK031(ki)006:713: rtsol med dbyig dang 'phrad par gyis //
NK031(ki)006:714: zhes pa la sogs pas bskul te /
NK031(ki)006:715: des thugs ka nas phyag na rdo rje phyung nas
NK031(ki)006:716: rin po che rab 'bar gyi 'khor lo phyag tu
NK031(ki)006:717: gtad nas / gnyis med ye shes gsang ba'i don //
NK031(ki)006:718: bya med mi rtsol ye sangs rgyas //
NK031(ki)006:719: dbu ma chen po drang po'i lam //
NK031(ki)006:720: 'dus pa'i tshogs la bstan par gyis //
NK031(ki)006:721: zhes khyod kyis rtsol med kyi theg pa ston cig par bskul bas /
NK031(ki)006:723: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK031(ki)006:724: tshig gi spyod yul ma yin pas //
NK031(ki)006:725: bdag gi 'gro bar shin tu dka' //
NK031(ki)006:726: ma rtogs pa la tshig sgo nas //
NK031(ki)006:727: mtshon nas rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:728: ci rig par ni rnam par 'gro //
NK031(ki)006:730: phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i rgyal ba la dri ba bzhis
NK031(ki)006:731: dris shing the tshom bcad de bka' bgros nas rdo
NK031(ki)006:732: ar mo li ka'i steng na gser gyi mchod rten
NK031(ki)006:733: bang rim bzhi pa srong zhing rdo rje rtse dgu
NK031(ki)006:735: 'od zer gyi zhags pas sems lhag can drangs nas 'khor lo'i steng du ni bzhag /
NK031(ki)006:736: phyag g.yas pa gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa de gdugs su phub nas /
NK031(ki)006:737: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang bskur srung bral rig pa'i dam tshig phog /
NK031(ki)006:738: rna brgyud sems kyi don bstan /
NK031(ki)006:739: dus mtha'i skad cig la klong dgu bam po nyi khri gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK031(ki)006:741: de nas sems dpa' rdo rjes zhus pas /
NK031(ki)006:742: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po lags //
NK031(ki)006:743: ston pa nyid kyang thig le spros med dam //
NK031(ki)006:745: dus dang gnas ni gcig pa ji lta bu //
NK031(ki)006:747: zhes pa'i bar tshig dgu zhus pas /
NK031(ki)006:748: de nas byang chub sems kun byed rgyal po des /
NK031(ki)006:749: sems dpa' rdo rje la 'di skad gsungs so //
NK031(ki)006:750: kye sems dpa' chen po yid sgra la chug shig /
NK031(ki)006:752: zhes pa nas zhes gsungs so //
NK031(ki)006:753: zhes pa'i bar gyis ston pas de dag thams cad
NK031(ki)006:754: thig le nyag gcig yin par le'u dang por lan
NK031(ki)006:755: btab / ston pa ci ston dang 'khor du 'khor
NK031(ki)006:756: ba'i don ci la 'khor ba la sogs pa'i lan
NK031(ki)006:757: le'u gsum par ston te zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa'o
NK031(ki)006:759: spyi don tha ma thugs rje skyes nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad tshul ni /
NK031(ki)006:761: nga ni thugs rje'i ngo bo ste //
NK031(ki)006:762: gang la dga' ba'i dus su ni //
NK031(ki)006:763: gang dga' ba yi don bya'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:764: nga yis byas pa'i don bstan gyis //
NK031(ki)006:765: sems dpa' rdo rje khyod nyon cig /
NK031(ki)006:768: rten can gyi don mdzad par 'dod pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:769: rten med kyis don mdzad par 'dod pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:770: ngo bo nyid kyis don mdzad par 'dod pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:773: zhing khams dang gzhal yas khang dang sku gsung thugs
NK031(ki)006:774: yon tan dang phrin las la sogs pa kun rdzob
NK031(ki)006:776: gdul bya'i don yang de nyid dam de la brten nas mdzad par 'dod pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:777: bram ze mchod sdong grub pa lta bu'o //
NK031(ki)006:778: de ni rgya gar na slob dpon seng ge bzang
NK031(ki)006:779: po dang bod kyi zhang shes par bla ma'i bzhed
NK031(ki)006:780: do // gnyis pa rten med ni /
NK031(ki)006:781: don dam du 'bras bu mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi
NK031(ki)006:782: sa na gzugs sku'i bkod pa phun pa dang a
NK031(ki)006:783: cang chos kyi / tha na rnam par mi rtog
NK031(ki)006:784: pa'i ye shes tsam yang ma grub ste ye shes
NK031(ki)006:786: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa tsam la sangs rgyas zhes 'dogs so //
NK031(ki)006:787: de yang rdo rje cod pan las /
NK031(ki)006:788: gang gis nga la gzugs su mthong //
NK031(ki)006:789: gang gis nga la sgrar shes pa //
NK031(ki)006:790: log par spong la zhugs pa ste //
NK031(ki)006:791: skye bo de yis nga mi mthong //
NK031(ki)006:792: 'dren pa rnams ni chos kyi sku //
NK031(ki)006:793: chos nyid gang yin sangs rgyas lta //
NK031(ki)006:795: 'on kyang 'gro ba'i don ni chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i go phye bas dang /
NK031(ki)006:796: gdul bya rang gi rgyud la dkar po'i phyogs kyi bag chags yod pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:797: sngon gyi smon lam gyi dbang gis gzugs skur snang nas don mdzad pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:798: drang srong dmod pa grub pa lta bu'o //
NK031(ki)006:799: de ni rgya gar na rgyu klu sgrub dang /
NK031(ki)006:800: bod kyi reng sgom chos bzang gis bzhed do //
NK031(ki)006:801: gsum pa ngo bo nyid kyi don byed par 'dod pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:802: sangs rgyas sku dang ye shes yod chos su sgros mi 'dogs /
NK031(ki)006:803: med chos su skur pa mi 'debs te sgro skur
NK031(ki)006:804: gyi mtha' dang bral bar dbyer med lhun grub chen
NK031(ki)006:805: po sangs rgyas zhes bya ste /
NK031(ki)006:806: de la don bya mi bya'i ris med kyang lhun
NK031(ki)006:807: grub kyi mdzad pa mi 'gog pa'i cha nas gdul
NK031(ki)006:808: bya'i don phyogs med du mos pa bzhin 'char ba
NK031(ki)006:809: ste / dper na nam mkha' tshon la dbyibs ris
NK031(ki)006:810: med kyang lung pa'i rkyen gyis sna tshogs su 'char
NK031(ki)006:811: ste / ba bzhin no // 'di nyid kyi brgyad pa las /
NK031(ki)006:812: ma sgrib rang byung ye shes ni //
NK031(ki)006:813: rgyu 'bras ston pa sku gsum snang //
NK031(ki)006:814: la lar rgyu'i ston par snang //
NK031(ki)006:815: la lar 'brel ba'i ston par snang //
NK031(ki)006:816: la lar 'bras bu'i ston par snang //
NK031(ki)006:819: bsam gyis mi khyab 'od gsal sems //
NK031(ki)006:820: 'gyur med dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK031(ki)006:821: rang snang lhun grub byin rlabs las //
NK031(ki)006:822: skal ldan bsam pa ji bzhin du //
NK031(ki)006:824: rang sems pad+ma ltar gnas la //
NK031(ki)006:825: gzhan dag ji ltar chos bzhin mdzad //
NK031(ki)006:826: g.yem par 'dod la g.yem pa nyid //
NK031(ki)006:827: zhe sdang mnar sems nga rgyal nyid //
NK031(ki)006:828: thabs nyid gsang ba'i lam du bstan //
NK031(ki)006:829: gang sems gang 'thad sgo dang bstun //
NK031(ki)006:832: ma bcos de bzhin nyid 'di las //
NK031(ki)006:833: yid bzhin cir yang 'byung ba ni //
NK031(ki)006:834: cho 'phrul snang ba'i sems can rnams //
NK031(ki)006:835: ji ltar 'dus pa'i mthong thos snang //
NK031(ki)006:837: de ni rgya gar na rgyal po dza dang bod na shes rab grags pa'i bzhed do //
NK031(ki)006:838: de yang da res tha ma 'dod pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:839: don mdzad tshul dngos la gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:840: blo rab cig char ba rnams la kun bzang gis
NK031(ki)006:841: rgyu 'bras 'das pa'i theg pas don mdzad pa dang
NK031(ki)006:842: / blo chung rim gyis pa rnams la sku gsum gyis rgyu 'bras kyi theg pas don mdzad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:843: de yang gang du bshad pas mngon no //
NK031(ki)006:845: ston pa kun bzang nyid kyis rgyu 'bras gnyis las
NK031(ki)006:846: 'das pa'i chos nyid byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK031(ki)006:847: ji lta ba bstan nas don mdzad pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:849: gcig la dga' ba de la ni //
NK031(ki)006:850: chos rnams gcig tu 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:851: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ste //
NK031(ki)006:852: sems kyi ngo bo kun byed bstan //
NK031(ki)006:854: gnas ni chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings nyid du /
NK031(ki)006:856: dus gsum dbyer med bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus
NK031(ki)006:857: su ston pa rang bzhin gyi ston pa kun tu
NK031(ki)006:858: bzang po rang 'byung gi bcom ldan 'das sems nyid
NK031(ki)006:859: rang 'byung gi ye shes bde ba chen po des
NK031(ki)006:860: / don gyi 'khor rang 'byung ye shes snang ba
NK031(ki)006:861: nyid las mi gzhan pa sangs rgyas sems can ma
NK031(ki)006:862: lus pa rnams la bstan pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:863: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kyi don rang chas su
NK031(ki)006:864: yod pa'i ro rang rang gi blo la gsal ba
NK031(ki)006:866: de yang bcu drug pa las /
NK031(ki)006:867: nga ni ye nas kun byed rgyal po yin //
NK031(ki)006:868: ston pa bstan pa 'khor dus ngas byas nas //
NK031(ki)006:869: ston pa'i ston pa yang ni nga yis byed //
NK031(ki)006:870: bstan pa nga yis rang bzhin de ston la //
NK031(ki)006:871: 'khor yang nga yi ngo bo de phyung nas //
NK031(ki)006:872: dus gnas nga yi rang bzhin de ru ni //
NK031(ki)006:873: kun byed nga yi rang bzhin bstan pa las //
NK031(ki)006:874: nga min chos ni gcig kyang bstan pa med //
NK031(ki)006:877: kun bzang rgyal ba mchog gi lha //
NK031(ki)006:878: byang chub sems kyi snying po yin //
NK031(ki)006:879: kun gyi ston pa byang chub sems //
NK031(ki)006:880: bstan pa byang chub snying po yin //
NK031(ki)006:881: chos nyid dbyings kyi gnas chen du //
NK031(ki)006:882: sangs rgyas sems can 'khor bsogs nas //
NK031(ki)006:883: snga phyi med par bstan pa ni //
NK031(ki)006:884: rang 'byung ye shes rig pa'i rgyal //
NK031(ki)006:886: de yang 'di nyid kyi rang gzhung bston pa chos
NK031(ki)006:887: ston te gtso so lnga pa dang gtan la 'bebs
NK031(ki)006:888: pa'i mdo lung gtso che yang don dbu zhabs thams
NK031(ki)006:889: cad nas ston par byed do //
NK031(ki)006:890: gnyis pa sku gsum ston pa'i rgyu 'bras kyis theg pas don mdzad pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:892: mtshan ma grangs la dga' ba la /
NK031(ki)006:893: kun byed rgyal pos byas pa yi //
NK031(ki)006:894: sna tshogs brjod kyis mi bstan pa //
NK031(ki)006:896: de nyid tshig chod du mi go ba rnams la
NK031(ki)006:897: kun byed rgyal po'i rang bzhin gsum las sku gsum
NK031(ki)006:898: du shar nas rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa rnams gang
NK031(ki)006:899: la gang 'tsham du gsungs pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:901: sku gsum sna tshogs byung nas ni //
NK031(ki)006:902: theg pa gsum gyi ngo yang ston //
NK031(ki)006:903: rgyu 'bras can ni des tshim byed //
NK031(ki)006:906: rdzogs chen skye med chos sku las //
NK031(ki)006:907: skye ba'i cho 'phrul tshul byung ba //
NK031(ki)006:908: longs spyod rdzogs sku sprul pa'i sku //
NK031(ki)006:909: sum brgyud dgu phrugs rnams sprul pa //
NK031(ki)006:910: tshig dang yi ge dgur grags te //
NK031(ki)006:911: theg pa rnam pa dgu ru bstan //
NK031(ki)006:913: de yang blo rab rnams la chos skus bskyed rdzogs gsum /
NK031(ki)006:914: 'bring la longs skus phyi rgyud gsum /
NK031(ki)006:915: tha ma la sprul skus mtshan nyid sde gsum gsungs pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:917: ston pa chos sku'i bstan pa 'di ltar te /
NK031(ki)006:918: gsang ba gsum gyi rang bzhin bstan pa ste //
NK031(ki)006:919: gzhi ma chos nyid dag gi rang bzhin las //
NK031(ki)006:920: gsang ba bskyed dang gsang ba rdzogs pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:921: gsang ba rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin gsum //
NK031(ki)006:922: kun gyi spyod yul ma yin gsang bar bshad /
NK031(ki)006:924: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i bstan pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:925: bya ba byed pa'i phyi ba sde gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:927: ston pa sprul pa sku yi bstan pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:928: nyan thos rang rgyal theg chen mdo sde gsum /
NK031(ki)006:929: phyi zhes mtshan nyid phyi pa zhes su bshad //
NK031(ki)006:932: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen gsum //
NK031(ki)006:933: chos kyi sku yi gsung du bshad //
NK031(ki)006:934: kri ya yo ga phyi nang gsum //
NK031(ki)006:935: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i gsung du grags //
NK031(ki)006:936: nyan thos rang rgyal mdo sde gsum //
NK031(ki)006:937: sprul pa sku yi gsung du grags //
NK031(ki)006:941: bshad rgyud kyi dgu mdos ston te /
NK031(ki)006:942: dngos su a nu man chad kyi sde snod tsho yin no //
NK031(ki)006:943: de dag gi bshad lugs ni /
NK031(ki)006:945: sku gsum ston pa gsum gyi bshad lugs ni //
NK031(ki)006:946: phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lnga nang du //
NK031(ki)006:947: chos kyi sku ni byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad //
NK031(ki)006:948: longs spyod rdzogs pa rang gi ngo bos ston //
NK031(ki)006:949: sprul pa'i sku ni don rnams tshig tu bsdeb //
NK031(ki)006:950: sku gsum ston pa'i bshad lugs rnam gsum yin //
NK031(ki)006:953: dang po chos sku byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:954: phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lnga nang du //
NK031(ki)006:956: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa chos sku rdo rje 'chang /
NK031(ki)006:959: gnas 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang /
NK031(ki)006:960: dus ston 'khor 'dzom pa'i dus su byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:962: ston pa longs sku kun rig rnam par snang mdzad /
NK031(ki)006:963: 'khor sa la gnas pa'i byang sems /
NK031(ki)006:964: bstan pa kri yog sde gsum /
NK031(ki)006:965: gnas 'og min gyi gnas ri rab ri yi rtse mor /
NK031(ki)006:967: rang gi ngo bos bshad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:969: ston pa sprul sku sh+aakya thub /
NK031(ki)006:971: bstan pa mtshan nyid sde gsum /
NK031(ki)006:972: gnas bya rgod phung po'i ri la sogs par /
NK031(ki)006:974: tshig dang don du sdeb nas bshad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:976: chos sku ye shes sku dang thugs rje'i sku //
NK031(ki)006:977: sku gsum gang gis 'dul ba'i ston sku la //
NK031(ki)006:978: nyid dang mthun pa'i gnas 'khor phun sum tshogs //
NK031(ki)006:980: de ltar yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de
NK031(ki)006:981: rnams kyis gsungs pa'i chos de dag kyang bsdu na
NK031(ki)006:986: byang chub sems ni ye nas rdzogs pa che //
NK031(ki)006:987: rdzogs pa chen po ye nas rgyu 'bras 'das //
NK031(ki)006:988: rgyu 'bras 'das pa'i bshad lugs bstan pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:989: kun byed byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin las //
NK031(ki)006:990: sku gsum ston pa byung ba'i bshad lugs dang //
NK031(ki)006:991: rnam pa gnyis kyis bshad lugs bstan pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:993: de las dang po rgyu 'bras 'das pa'i theg pa la dbye ba med de /
NK031(ki)006:994: der theg pa thams cad ro gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK031(ki)006:995: gnyis pa rgyu 'bras kyi chos la dbye na gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:996: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:999: mya ngan 'das pa'i theg pa la //
NK031(ki)006:1000: rnam pa gnyis su dbye bar bya //
NK031(ki)006:1001: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1004: rgyu theg pa la gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1006: mtshan nyid rgyu la rnam pa gsum //
NK031(ki)006:1007: sdug bsngal spong ba'i nyan thos dang //
NK031(ki)006:1008: shes pa 'gegs pa'i rang rgyal dang //
NK031(ki)006:1009: rnam rtog sbyong ba'i sde pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1011: 'bras bu theg pa la dbye lugs gnyis las /
NK031(ki)006:1012: bshad rgyud ltar na gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1014: 'bras bu'i theg pa la ni gsum //
NK031(ki)006:1015: bya ba'i sde dang gnyis ka'i ste //
NK031(ki)006:1016: rnal 'byor ba dang rnam pa gsum //
NK031(ki)006:1020: rnal 'byor pa la rnam pa gnyis //
NK031(ki)006:1021: phyi pa dang ni nang pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1023: nang pa la bskyed rdzogs gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1025: nang pa'i rnal 'byor rnam pa gsum //
NK031(ki)006:1026: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen gsum //
NK031(ki)006:1028: gnyis pa rtsa rgyud ltar nang 'bras bu'i theg pa la gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:1030: phyi pa la u pa zhor la btang bas kri yog gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:1032: rdo rje de sgrib phyi pa gnyis //
NK031(ki)006:1033: sku dang gsung thugs ye shes ni //
NK031(ki)006:1034: blang dor byas pa'i sgo nas ni //
NK031(ki)006:1035: chu zla bzhin du grub par 'dod //
NK031(ki)006:1037: nang pa la bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1038: blang dor med pa'i nang pa ni //
NK031(ki)006:1039: rim pa gsum dang snying po yis //
NK031(ki)006:1040: bdag nyid dbyings dang ye shes lta //
NK031(ki)006:1041: gang la'ang mi brten bya med 'di //
NK031(ki)006:1042: kun gyi snying por gyur pas na //
NK031(ki)006:1043: bya ba med pa'i phrin las 'das //
NK031(ki)006:1045: de ltar rgyu 'bras kyi chos la phye bas theg pa rim pa dgur byung ste bgrang /
NK031(ki)006:1047: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK031(ki)006:1049: de dag kyang bsdu na rdzogs pa chen por 'du ste /
NK031(ki)006:1053: rdzogs pa chen po la rgya gar du grags tshod du //
NK031(ki)006:1054: nges par klong chen po dgu /
NK031(ki)006:1056: bam po brgyad khri bzhi stong du grags /
NK031(ki)006:1057: 'bring du klong dgu bam po nyi khrir grags /
NK031(ki)006:1059: spyi rgyud badz+ra kha sa man+ta nam mkha' dang dang
NK031(ki)006:1060: mnyam pa'i yi ge med pa'i rgyud zhes bya ba
NK031(ki)006:1062: stod sems nyid mtha' dang mnyam pa bar rig pa mtha' dang mnyam pa /
NK031(ki)006:1063: smad ye shes mtha' dang mnyam par ston pa gcig bzhugs skad /
NK031(ki)006:1066: rmad du byung ba dang bdun /
NK031(ki)006:1068: rmad du byung ba dang bdun /
NK031(ki)006:1070: rmad du byung ba dang bdun du byung ba'o //
NK031(ki)006:1072: 'on kyang bod du grags tshod kyi dbang byas na /
NK031(ki)006:1073: be ro tsa na'i sku drin la brgyud pa dang po dang /
NK031(ki)006:1075: tha ma gsum du grags te /
NK031(ki)006:1076: de rnams so so rang rang gi sa dbye sgo
NK031(ki)006:1077: mi mthun pa tha dad pa du ma yod kyis
NK031(ki)006:1078: kyang / da res brgyud pa tha ma'i dbang du dbye na /
NK031(ki)006:1079: spyir rdzogs pa chen po la /
NK031(ki)006:1086: dang po rgyud sde la mar pa khrom rgyal gyis
NK031(ki)006:1087: slob ma mi gsum la bzhed lugs gsum du byung
NK031(ki)006:1088: ste / gsum pa dbang tshul gyi bzhed pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1089: na rog ston pa'i bzhed pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1090: mar chung shes rab 'od bzhed do //
NK031(ki)006:1092: gsang rdzogs 'od dang gsum po ti ser chung dang bzhi'o //
NK031(ki)006:1093: na rog ston pa'i bzhed ltar na lnga ste /
NK031(ki)006:1094: badz+ra kha sa man+ta nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1095: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' mnyam klong gi rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1096: nam mkha' che rgyas pa'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1097: rmad du byung ba'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1098: khu byug rig pa kun bzang mdzod kyi rgyud do //
NK031(ki)006:1100: lta ba mtha' dbus med pa nam mkha' ltar ston pa'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1101: rdo rje snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud do /
NK031(ki)006:1103: rtsa ba'i rgyud dang rgyud phyi ma dang /
NK031(ki)006:1106: rdo rje snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud la gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1107: rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:1108: ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1109: ye shes klong rdzogs kyi rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1110: de rnams spyi'i bshad rgyud badz+ra kha sa man+ta chen mo'o //
NK031(ki)006:1111: gnyis pa rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' mnyam klong gi rgyud la dbye ba med do //
NK031(ki)006:1112: gsum pa nam mkha' che rgyas pa'i rgyud la gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:1113: rgyas pa rtsa ba'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1115: bzhi pa rmad du byung ba'i rgyud sde la spyir le'u 'bum phrag gcig bzhugs na'ang /
NK031(ki)006:1116: bod du 'gyur ba la gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1117: rgyas pa le'u brgyad cu rtsa bzhi pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1120: lnga pa khu byung rig pa kun bzang mdzad kyi rgyud la gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1121: spyi rgyud chen mo bzhi dang /
NK031(ki)006:1122: bshad pa'i rgyud bco brgyad dang /
NK031(ki)006:1123: man ngag gi rgyud gcig go //
NK031(ki)006:1125: nam mkha' dri ma med pa gsang ba'i sgo mngas kyi rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1126: 'khor lo gting rdzogs rgyal po'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1127: spyod pa bsdus pa sgron ma rgyal po'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1128: nya mo bag la nyal gyi rgyud do //
NK031(ki)006:1129: mar chung shes rab 'od kyi bzhed pa la'ang lnga ste /
NK031(ki)006:1130: nam mkha' che rgyas pa'i rgyud sde gsang ba'i snying
NK031(ki)006:1131: po yi ge med pa'i gdam ngag dang bcas pa
NK031(ki)006:1132: dang / rdo rje sems dpa' mkha' mnyam klong gi
NK031(ki)006:1133: rgyud sde nam mkha' dri ma med pa gsang ba
NK031(ki)006:1134: sgo mngas kyi gdams ngag dang bcas pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1135: khu byug rig pa kun bzang mdzod kyi rgyud sde
NK031(ki)006:1136: rtsa ba bco brgyad kyi man ngag dang bcas pa
NK031(ki)006:1137: dang / byang chub kyi sems rmad du byung ba'i
NK031(ki)006:1138: rgyud sde ma bu sum skor gyi gdam ngag dang
NK031(ki)006:1139: dang / bcas pa dang / byang chub kyi sems
NK031(ki)006:1140: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud sde ma bu
NK031(ki)006:1141: dgu skor gyi gdam ngag dang bcas pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1143: rgyas pa rtsa ba'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1145: yi ge med pa zhes bya ba'i snyan rgyud kyi gdam ngag dang bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK031(ki)006:1146: gnyis pa la dbye ba ni rgyud chen po gcig bzhugs te /
NK031(ki)006:1147: de la gdams kyang lam dkyus ma'i gdam ngag la
NK031(ki)006:1148: brten nas 'gro ba phyogs med du drang pa zhes
NK031(ki)006:1149: bya ste / gang zag lta ba ma rtogs pa brgya tham pa la rtogs thabs brgya tham pa /
NK031(ki)006:1150: sems ma zin pa brgya tham pa la gzung thabs brgya tham pa /
NK031(ki)006:1151: skyon byung ba brgya tham pa la bcos thabs brgya tham pa ston pa bzhugs so //
NK031(ki)006:1153: rtsa ba bco brgyad la rgyab brten gyi rgyud bco
NK031(ki)006:1154: brgyad bzhugs te man ngag rtsa ba bco brgyad pa
NK031(ki)006:1155: nyid do // bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1156: rgyas pa le'u bzhi bcu pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1158: bsdus pa bcu gcig pa'am bzhi pa gsum snyan rgyud kyi gdam ngag dang bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK031(ki)006:1160: rdo rje snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud sde dang /
NK031(ki)006:1161: lta ba nam mkha' ltar mtha' dbus med pa'i rgyud sde'o //
NK031(ki)006:1163: man ngag gi rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:1164: de'i bshad pa'i rgyud badz+ra kha sa man+ta nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1165: sgom pa'i rgyud ye shes rdzogs pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1166: bsam bstan gyi rnyog ma sel ba'i rgyud e a ra li rnyog ma med pa'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1167: rnal 'byor gyi nyams rnyed pa'i rgyud nya mo bag la nyal gyi rgyud sde'o //
NK031(ki)006:1168: gzhan yang rdo rje snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i
NK031(ki)006:1169: rgyud kyi khong su 'gro ba'i ye shes bdun 'byung
NK031(ki)006:1170: gi rgyud dang / klong dgu'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1171: rin po che 'khor lo ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1172: kun 'dus 'od kyi tan+t+ra la sogs pa 'ga' bzhugs so //
NK031(ki)006:1173: gzhan yang rdo rje snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud sde bcu gsum /
NK031(ki)006:1174: pad+ma'i snying po gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud sde bcu gsum /
NK031(ki)006:1175: de gnyis bsdebs nas nyams su len pa'i snyan rgyud bcu gsum ste /
NK031(ki)006:1176: so dgu po de rnams la rgyud mtha'i mthar thug tu byed pa yang yod gsung skad do //
NK031(ki)006:1177: gnyis pa mtha' dbus med 'di rgyud la dgu ste /
NK031(ki)006:1178: kun byed rgyal po rtsa ba'i rgyud dang /
NK031(ki)006:1182: spyi'i rgyud sde bzhi zhes bya ste nam mkha' dang mnyam pa yi ge med pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1183: rgya mtsho dang mnyam pa rnyog pa med pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1184: nyi zla dang mnyam pa dri ma med pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1185: rin po che dang mnyam pa skye ba med pa'i rgyud do //
NK031(ki)006:1186: phyi ma gsang ba mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud dang dagu'o //
NK031(ki)006:1187: gnyis pa sems sde'i skor ni /
NK031(ki)006:1188: yongs su grags pa'i sems sde bco brgyad dang sems phran drug cu rtsa bzhi'am /
NK031(ki)006:1189: brgyad cu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa bzhugs so //
NK031(ki)006:1190: gsum pa klong sde skor la gnyis te /
NK031(ki)006:1191: bstan pa'i klong dang man ngag gi klong ngos /
NK031(ki)006:1192: dang po ni klong dgu phrugs dang /
NK031(ki)006:1196: thugs rje klong nag po la sogs pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1198: rtsa ba rgya mtsho'i klong la a tsa ra gsal ba rgyan gyi bshad 'grel dang /
NK031(ki)006:1200: snyan rgyud kyi gdams pa dang bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK031(ki)006:1201: bzhi pa bsam bstan gyi sde ni /
NK031(ki)006:1202: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes mdzad pa'i sgom pa'i yi ge phrag brgyad cu ste /
NK031(ki)006:1203: re res kyang gang zag re re'i cha rkyen tshang bar ston pa bzhugs skad do //
NK031(ki)006:1204: lnga pa dbang gi sde ni /
NK031(ki)006:1205: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang ston pa'i dbang gi chos sde rnam pa lnga ste /
NK031(ki)006:1210: de ltar chos sde lnga las /
NK031(ki)006:1211: de res rgyud sder ngos gzung /
NK031(ki)006:1212: rgyud sde rang la lnga yod pa las /
NK031(ki)006:1213: 'di byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud sde /
NK031(ki)006:1215: lta ba mtha' dbus med pa nam mkha' ltar ston pa'i rgyud sde'o //
NK031(ki)006:1216: de la'ang dgu las rtsa ba'i rgyud kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud du ngos gzung ngo //
NK031(ki)006:1217: de dag ni bstan pa spyi ltar khog dbub pa
NK031(ki)006:1218: dam pa'i chos ngos gzung thabs dang bcas pa zhes
NK031(ki)006:1219: bya ste / dper na sman pa 'tsho byed gzhon
NK031(ki)006:1220: nus lag gi rtsa dang lus kyi chu la brten
NK031(ki)006:1221: nas lus mgo mjug gi nad ngos 'dzi na lta
NK031(ki)006:1222: bya ste / bu'o // spyi don gnyis pa rgyud
NK031(ki)006:1223: 'di nyid kyi gnas tshul ltar khog dbub pa la
NK031(ki)006:1224: bya ste / bu'o // gnyis te / rgyud 'di gzhan las khyad par 'phags pa'i che ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:1225: che ba dang ldan pa'i rgyud de ji ltar bshad pa'i thabs kyi yan lag go //
NK031(ki)006:1226: dang po la dagu'am bdun te /
NK031(ki)006:1227: lung thams cad kyi rgyal po yin par nges pa'i che ba rgyal po'i bka' lung lta bu dang /
NK031(ki)006:1228: spyir a nu man chad la'ang rang rang gi thad
NK031(ki)006:1229: ka'i don gtan la 'bebs shing sgro skur dang bral
NK031(ki)006:1230: ba'i lung re yod pas na rgyal po ma lag
NK031(ki)006:1231: ste cha sa nyid kyi phyogs 'ga' las gtan la
NK031(ki)006:1233: 'di ni gnas lugs chad lhag med par gtan la
NK031(ki)006:1234: 'bebs pa sgro skur mtha' dag dang bral bas gsung
NK031(ki)006:1235: thams cad kyi rgyal po ste dper na rgyal po'i
NK031(ki)006:1236: bka' lung la gzhan gyis skyor mi nus pa lta
NK031(ki)006:1237: bu'o // de yang bcu gnyis pa lung khung brtan /
NK031(ki)006:1239: kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems nga ni //
NK031(ki)006:1240: lung chen kun gyi rgyal po nga yin pas //
NK031(ki)006:1241: ston pa gsum yang dang por nga las byung //
NK031(ki)006:1242: lung zhes bya ba ston pa'i bka' la gdags //
NK031(ki)006:1244: man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin par nges
NK031(ki)006:1245: pa'i che ba gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bu dang
NK031(ki)006:1246: / spyir a nu man chad la'ang rang rang gi
NK031(ki)006:1247: tshogs chung zhing don che ba'i man ngag re yod
NK031(ki)006:1248: kyang thams cad sems nyid du la ma zlos pas
NK031(ki)006:1249: rtsa ba min la 'di ni gnas lugs thabs su
NK031(ki)006:1250: khyer bas tshegs chung don che gnad du brdeg pa'i
NK031(ki)006:1251: phyir na'am thams cad sems nyid du la zlos pa'i
NK031(ki)006:1252: phyir man ngag gi rtsa ba zhes bya ste dper
NK031(ki)006:1253: na gser 'gyur gyi rtsis lcags ma spangs gser du
NK031(ki)006:1256: man ngag kun gyi rtsa ba nga yin pas //
NK031(ki)006:1257: sems las ma gtogs pa yi chos nyid ni //
NK031(ki)006:1258: dus gsum bud+ha khams gsum sems can la //
NK031(ki)006:1259: kun byed nga yis yang dag bstan pa med //
NK031(ki)006:1261: rgyud dang mdo sde kun gyi spyi 'grel yin par
NK031(ki)006:1262: nges pa'i che ba 'phrul gyi me long lta bu
NK031(ki)006:1263: dang / a nu man chad ni rang rang gi
NK031(ki)006:1264: 'dod pa tsho dang phyogs snga kha yar las mi
NK031(ki)006:1265: khrol bas spyi'i 'grel ba ma yin la /
NK031(ki)006:1266: 'di ni theg pa mtha' dag gi don gsal bar
NK031(ki)006:1267: 'grel bas gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde dang mdo sde
NK031(ki)006:1268: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa mtha' dag gi spyi'i 'grel
NK031(ki)006:1270: dper na 'phrul gyi me long gis kun gsal bar mthong ba lta bu'o //
NK031(ki)006:1272: rgyud dang mdo sde kun gyi spyi 'grel yin //
NK031(ki)006:1273: rgyud dang mdo sde ston pa'i ston pa yang //
NK031(ki)006:1274: kun byed nga rang rang bzhin byung ba yin //
NK031(ki)006:1275: ston pa dang ni bstan pa gnyis ka 'grel //
NK031(ki)006:1277: bstan pa thams cad kyi yang rtse yin par nges
NK031(ki)006:1278: pa'i che ba ri rgyal lhun po'i rtser phyin pa
NK031(ki)006:1279: lta bu dang / sku gsum gyi bstan pa rtsol
NK031(ki)006:1280: bcas thams cad theg pa brgyad po'i rtse mo'i rgyud
NK031(ki)006:1281: lung gnyis yin la de gnyis kyi yang rtse mor
NK031(ki)006:1282: gyur pa a ti yin 'di nyid gzhan gyi spyod
NK031(ki)006:1283: yul du ma gyur la khams 'og tu kun chub
NK031(ki)006:1284: pas na bstan pa thams cad kyi yang rtse zhes
NK031(ki)006:1285: lta bu dang / bya ste / dper na ri
NK031(ki)006:1286: rgyal lhun po de gser gyi ri bdun la sogs
NK031(ki)006:1287: pa ri phran yongs las 'phags pa lta bu'o //
NK031(ki)006:1289: kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems nga ni //
NK031(ki)006:1290: bstan pa kun gyi rgyal po yin par bshad //
NK031(ki)006:1291: nga las byung ba'i ston pa sku gsum gyis //
NK031(ki)006:1292: bstan pa mdo sde 'dul ba mngon pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1293: bstan pa so so'i sde ni 'bum sde dang //
NK031(ki)006:1294: bskyed rdzogs gsang ba la sogs rtsol sgrub can //
NK031(ki)006:1295: kun kyang rtsol sgrub 'das pa nga la bkrod //
NK031(ki)006:1296: rtsol sgrub nyid kyis 'das pa nga mi mthong //
NK031(ki)006:1297: des na bstan pa kun gyi yang rtser bshad //
NK031(ki)006:1299: theg pa thams cad kyi nying khu yin par nges
NK031(ki)006:1300: pa'i che ba mar gyi yang zhun lta bu dang
NK031(ki)006:1301: / a nu man chad lam 'bras bu dang bcas
NK031(ki)006:1302: pa'i theg pa thams cad yin yang nyid khu ma
NK031(ki)006:1303: yin te drang don gtso cher ston pa'i phyir ro
NK031(ki)006:1304: / // 'di ni theg pa thams cad kyi nying
NK031(ki)006:1305: khu yin te thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa dang
NK031(ki)006:1306: nges don sel med du ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK031(ki)006:1307: dper na mar gyi yang zhun nam chang gi nying khu la sel med pa lta bu'o //
NK031(ki)006:1309: kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems nga ni //
NK031(ki)006:1310: theg pa kun gyi snying khu yin par bshad //
NK031(ki)006:1311: ston pa gsum gyi gnas pa'i theg pa gsum //
NK031(ki)006:1312: nges par gnas pa theg pa gcig las med //
NK031(ki)006:1313: gcig gi kun byed byang chub sems kyi sang //
NK031(ki)006:1314: de ni theg pa kun gyi nying khu bshad //
NK031(ki)006:1316: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel zhing ye shes chen
NK031(ki)006:1317: po'i snang ba mchod par nges pa'i che ba gzi
NK031(ki)006:1318: ldan nyi ma'i snying po lta bu dang /
NK031(ki)006:1319: skye ba dang 'gogs pa'i rgyud la yod pa'i lhan
NK031(ki)006:1320: cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang rang bzhin dang
NK031(ki)006:1321: ched du brtags pa'i mun pa thams cad skye 'gag
NK031(ki)006:1322: gnyis med kyi ngang du rang grol du zhing cir
NK031(ki)006:1323: snang rang ye yin pa la yin par rtogs pa'i
NK031(ki)006:1324: ye shes chen po'i snang ba gdul bya'i blo la
NK031(ki)006:1325: mched par byed pa ste dper na nyi zla'i man+dala
NK031(ki)006:1326: shar bas gling bzhi'i mun pa sel zhing snang ba
NK031(ki)006:1329: kye nga ni ma rig pa yi mun bsal nas //
NK031(ki)006:1330: ye shes chen po'i snang ba mched par byed //
NK031(ki)006:1332: ji lta bu zhes bstan zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:1333: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK031(ki)006:1334: bo d+hi de bzhin nyid du ma rig ste //
NK031(ki)006:1335: ma rig rtog pa'i mun pa 'thibs pa la //
NK031(ki)006:1336: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK031(ki)006:1337: kun byed b+ho d+hi tsi yis byas pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:1338: kun byed b+ho d+hi tsi tar rig byas nas //
NK031(ki)006:1339: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK031(ki)006:1340: so sor rtog pa'i mun pa bsal nas kyang //
NK031(ki)006:1341: rang byung ye shes chen po'i snang ba mched //
NK031(ki)006:1342: des na ma rig mun sel snang ba mched ces bya //
NK031(ki)006:1344: rnam par rtog pa'i dra ba 'dral zhing nyon mongs
NK031(ki)006:1345: pa'i phreng thag gcod par nges pa'i che ba ral
NK031(ki)006:1347: skye bo'i dus gsum gyi rtog pa mang la 'grel
NK031(ki)006:1348: ba'i dra ba dang der yang ma zad de theg
NK031(ki)006:1349: pa'i 'dod yon dug lnga la spong 'gegs sbyong skur
NK031(ki)006:1350: la sogs pa'i rtog pa mang la 'brel ba'i dra
NK031(ki)006:1351: ba thams cad 'dir rang grol du 'dral zhing /
NK031(ki)006:1352: skye bo'i 'dod chags rgyun dang bcas pa la sogs
NK031(ki)006:1353: pa'i nyon mongs pa'i phreng thag thams cad dang der
NK031(ki)006:1354: yang ma zad de theg pa 'og ma rnams de
NK031(ki)006:1355: ltar spong 'gegs sbyong sgyur la sogs pa'i rtsol bas
NK031(ki)006:1356: shes rgyud tshi chad pa'i nyon mongs pa'i phreng thag
NK031(ki)006:1357: kyang gshis rtsol sgrub bya rtsol thams cad dang bral
NK031(ki)006:1358: bar rtogs pa'i rang grol du gcod pa ste dper
NK031(ki)006:1359: na ral gri kha mngas kyi sos phyogs med du
NK031(ki)006:1363: rnam par rtog pa'i dra ba dral nas ni //
NK031(ki)006:1364: nyon mongs pa yi 'phreng thag gcod par byed //
NK031(ki)006:1365: ji ltar snang ba'i chos 'di thams cad la //
NK031(ki)006:1366: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa can rnams la //
NK031(ki)006:1367: la la dug mthong spong ba'i rtog pa byed //
NK031(ki)006:1368: la las sems chags pa yi yul mthong nas //
NK031(ki)006:1369: bden gnyis ma chags pa yi rtog pa byed //
NK031(ki)006:1370: la las rnam dag bya ba'i yul mthong nas //
NK031(ki)006:1371: dag pa gsum dang byin rlabs cho 'khrul gyis //
NK031(ki)006:1372: rje dang khol gyi tshul du rtog par byed //
NK031(ki)006:1373: la las rang rgyud dag pa'i man+dalara //
NK031(ki)006:1374: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhis sgrub 'dod rtogs byed pa //
NK031(ki)006:1375: thams cad kun byed b+ho d+hi tsi ta yis //
NK031(ki)006:1376: sems las gzhan ma yin rtog dral nas ni //
NK031(ki)006:1377: so sor rtog pa'i nyon mongs phreng thag gcod //
NK031(ki)006:1379: gnyis pa che ba de dang ldan pa'i rgyud kyi ji ltar bshad pa'i thabs kyi yan lag ni /
NK031(ki)006:1380: 'di nyid kyi bcu gsum pa las /
NK031(ki)006:1381: nga ni chos kyi spyi lung yin pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:1382: gtan tshig don gyi bshad lugs rnam lnga ni //
NK031(ki)006:1383: spyi don rnam pa lnga yis bshad pa ste //
NK031(ki)006:1384: lo rgyus don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1385: rtsa ba don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1386: yo ga don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1387: dgos pa don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1388: tshig gi don gyi bshad lugs bstan pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1392: de las dang po byung tshul lo rgyus kyi don gyis bshad pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:1394: dang por yid ches pa yi khungs bstan phyir //
NK031(ki)006:1395: lo rgyus don gyi bshad lugs bstan par bya //
NK031(ki)006:1399: lo rgyus don la rnam gsum ste //
NK031(ki)006:1400: byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1401: rang gi ngo bos bshad pa dang //
NK031(ki)006:1402: tshig sdebs la legs pa'i bshad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1404: de las dang po byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:1405: ston pa kun tu bzang pos rdo rje sems dpa' la bshad pa yin te /
NK031(ki)006:1407: byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad pa ni //
NK031(ki)006:1408: rang bzhin chos kyi gzhal yas na //
NK031(ki)006:1409: ston pa kun tu bzang po yang //
NK031(ki)006:1410: mtshan ma'i sku gsung mi mnga' bar //
NK031(ki)006:1411: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK031(ki)006:1412: bzang ngan blang dor med pa ru //
NK031(ki)006:1413: kun bzang nyid du byin rlabs nas //
NK031(ki)006:1414: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs la brgyud //
NK031(ki)006:1415: byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad ces bya //
NK031(ki)006:1417: gnyis pa rang gi ngo bos bshad pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:1418: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' dga' rab rdo rje la bshad pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:1420: rang gi ngo bos bshad pa ni //
NK031(ki)006:1421: skye med dbyings kyi pho brang na //
NK031(ki)006:1422: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' yang //
NK031(ki)006:1423: mtshan ma'i sku gsung mi mnga' bar //
NK031(ki)006:1424: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK031(ki)006:1425: skye 'jig med pa'i ngo bo dang //
NK031(ki)006:1426: rdo rje nga yi ngo bo ru //
NK031(ki)006:1427: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan la //
NK031(ki)006:1428: rig pa'i 'og min gnas su bshad //
NK031(ki)006:1429: rang gi ngo bos bshad ces bya //
NK031(ki)006:1431: gsum pa tshig sdebs legs pa'i bshad pa ni /
NK031(ki)006:1432: dga' rab rdo rjes 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sogs
NK031(ki)006:1433: pa la tshigs nyung la don che bar bshad pa
NK031(ki)006:1435: tshig sdebs legs pa'i bshad pa ni //
NK031(ki)006:1437: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan des //
NK031(ki)006:1438: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK031(ki)006:1439: skye ba med pa'i tshig brjod pas //
NK031(ki)006:1440: skye ba med pa'i don rtags su //
NK031(ki)006:1441: rin chen gser gyi glegs bam la //
NK031(ki)006:1442: bee d+aur zhun ma'i rang nan gyis //
NK031(ki)006:1443: tshig dang yi ger bris sdebs nas //
NK031(ki)006:1444: phyi rabs rnams kyi btsas su bzhag /
NK031(ki)006:1445: tshig sdebs legs pa'i bshad ces bya //
NK031(ki)006:1447: 'o na rdo rje sems dpa' dga' rab rdo rje la gnas gang du bshad pa yin zhe na /
NK031(ki)006:1448: rdo rje zam pa che chung dang po ye shes
NK031(ki)006:1449: gsang ba la sogs pa nas sum cu rtsa gsum
NK031(ki)006:1451: de'ang sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas na dga' rab
NK031(ki)006:1452: rdo rje sprul pa'i sku de nyid lha'i bu kun
NK031(ki)006:1453: dga' snying po sems lhag can du bzhugs pa'i dus
NK031(ki)006:1454: na sprul pa'i brgya byin gyis phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba
NK031(ki)006:1455: rnams la bskul / rgyal ba rnams kyi sems dpa' rdo rje la bskul /
NK031(ki)006:1456: des gsang bdag phyung ste de gnyis tha dad med
NK031(ki)006:1457: pas lha'i bu kun dga' snying po la bshad pa
NK031(ki)006:1458: ste / zhib tu thugs rje skye tshul gyi skabs ltar ro //
NK031(ki)006:1459: de yang rna rgyud rdo rje zam pa las /
NK031(ki)006:1460: dga' rab rdo rje bdag nyid kyang //
NK031(ki)006:1461: de ba bzang skyong bu thu bo //
NK031(ki)006:1462: kun dga' snying po bya ba yin //
NK031(ki)006:1465: sum cu rtsagasuma yang thog tu //
NK031(ki)006:1466: srog shing rdo rje rtse dgu par //
NK031(ki)006:1468: gsang ba'i gter 'dzin bdag por grags //
NK031(ki)006:1471: dus mtha'i skad cig nyid la ni //
NK031(ki)006:1472: rgyal thabs spyi blugs dbang bskur nas //
NK031(ki)006:1473: klong dgu bam po nyi khri gsungs //
NK031(ki)006:1474: 'dzam gling rgyud du rgyal thebs byas //
NK031(ki)006:1476: de ltar lha'i gnas su grags nas mi yul du dga' rab rdo rjes bshad pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:1477: de la spyi blug sras gcig la brgyud pa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1480: nyi shu rtsa gcig la brgyud pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1481: dang po ni 'jam dpal bshes gnyen kho na la bshad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1482: gnyis pa ni bram ze bde mchog snying po /
NK031(ki)006:1483: rgyal po d+ha he na ta lo /
NK031(ki)006:1484: blon po gang ba bzang po'i bu a tsat+ya a lo ke dang gsum bshad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1487: rgyal po d+ha he na ta lo dang /
NK031(ki)006:1489: khyi'i rgyal po ku ku ra dza dang /
NK031(ki)006:1490: lha'i rgyal po ma h+aa ra tsa dang /
NK031(ki)006:1492: sh+r+ai seng ha dang bdun la bshad pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1493: bzhi pa ni 'jam dpal bshes gnyen nas gri seng+ha'i
NK031(ki)006:1494: ma b+hi ma la yan chad la dus gcig tu
NK031(ki)006:1495: brgyud pa'o // de las da res kyi 'di bdun la brgyud pa'i lugs yin te /
NK031(ki)006:1496: de yang gzhan drug po ni sgom chen du dbang bskur la /
NK031(ki)006:1497: sh+r+ai seng+ha ni rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ro //
NK031(ki)006:1498: de yan chad rgya gar du brgyud pa'i tshul lo //
NK031(ki)006:1499: de nas rdzogs pa chen po 'di mnga' ris bod
NK031(ki)006:1500: kyi rgyal khams su ji ltar dar zhing brgyud pa'i
NK031(ki)006:1501: tshul ni / sh+r+ai seng+hasa bee ro tsa na la bshad pa ste /
NK031(ki)006:1502: de yang spyir rje me dbon rnam pa gsum gyi sku drin la dam pa chos kyi dbu snyems /
NK031(ki)006:1503: srol gtod dar zhing rgyas par mdzad de /
NK031(ki)006:1504: lha tho tho ring snyan shar gyi sku ring la
NK031(ki)006:1505: bde bar gshegs pa'i byin rlabs kyis bod mun pa'i
NK031(ki)006:1506: gangs bar srin po gdong dmar gyi yul 'dir /
NK031(ki)006:1507: rgya nag gi yul nas pam kong phyag rgya ba rnyed nas /
NK031(ki)006:1508: de la bkur sti dang rim gro byas pas rje sku tshe ring ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:1509: 'khor bkra shis pa dang chab srid mtho zhing mnga' thang rgyas par gyur pa'o //
NK031(ki)006:1510: de nas gdung rabs 'ga' zung nas mnga' bdag srong btsan sgam po'i sku drin la /
NK031(ki)006:1511: lo ts+aa ba kha che a nan+ta zhes bya bas sgra rang 'gyur du bsgyur nas /
NK031(ki)006:1512: dam pa'i chos dge ba bcu dang /
NK031(ki)006:1513: gzungs tsin d+ha ma ni dang /
NK031(ki)006:1515: dkon mchog sprin la sogs pa yang bsgyur ro //
NK031(ki)006:1516: de nas gdung rabs 'ga' na rje khri srong lde btsan gyi sku drin la /
NK031(ki)006:1517: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa bo d+hi sa t+wa dang
NK031(ki)006:1518: o rgyan gyi mkhas pa pad+ma sam b+ha ba dang
NK031(ki)006:1519: / bal po'i mkhas pa ka tu na pa kri dang /
NK031(ki)006:1520: rgya nag gi mkhas pa ha shang ma h+aa ya
NK031(ki)006:1521: na la sogs pa pan di ta mkhas pa mang
NK031(ki)006:1523: dam pa'i chos dpag tu med pa bsgyur /
NK031(ki)006:1524: thugs dam gyi rten dpal bsam yas dbu rtse rigs
NK031(ki)006:1525: gsum la sogs pa gtsug lag khang brgya rtsa brgyad
NK031(ki)006:1527: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la sogs pa la /
NK031(ki)006:1528: la zlo'i chos zhus pas blo ma khengs nas /
NK031(ki)006:1529: blon 'bangs rnams la rgyu 'bras la zlo ba'i chos tshol du btang bar bka' rtsal ba'i dus su /
NK031(ki)006:1530: pha ba gor he 'dod ces bya ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:1531: ma khri zhi za sgron skyid gnyis kyi bu pa gor ga 'jag tang zhes bya ba dang /
NK031(ki)006:1532: rtsangs the len ne len ta'i bu rtsang le gnyis na re /
NK031(ki)006:1533: rje yis bka' rtsal ba'i go bdag cag gnyis kyis dgum lags so zer nas /
NK031(ki)006:1534: stag gi lo dpyid zla ra ba'i tshes gsum la gza' zla ba la gtad nas /
NK031(ki)006:1535: lho phyogs me'i thog tu phyin te /
NK031(ki)006:1536: de yang gser phye ba men gyi ra do /
NK031(ki)006:1537: gser gyi pa tra mdzub gang pa re khyer nas ar+ya pa lo'i gling du spags so //
NK031(ki)006:1538: der thugs rje chen po'i lung thob nas /
NK031(ki)006:1539: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyis 'phrang srung las thar te /
NK031(ki)006:1540: zla ba gnyis kyis rgya gar yul du rdol te /
NK031(ki)006:1541: spyir rgya gar gyi yul na chos kyi babs so chen po bzhi yod pa las /
NK031(ki)006:1542: rgya gar rdo rje gdan bya rgod phung po'i ri dbu rgyan rdo rje'i phug /
NK031(ki)006:1543: 'bri ka ma la sh+ai la'i gtsug lag khang dang bzhi gsungs /
NK031(ki)006:1547: byang phyogs sa la'i yul dang bzhir zung ngams /
NK031(ki)006:1548: 'bri ka ma la shi la'i gtsug lag khang du
NK031(ki)006:1549: mi rnams la zhag du mar dri ba bzhi dris
NK031(ki)006:1553: thug pa ni gang yin zhes dris pas /
NK031(ki)006:1554: thams cad na re mgrin gcig tu slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha zhes bya ba /
NK031(ki)006:1555: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga la gtugs pa /
NK031(ki)006:1557: dgung lo lnga brgya lon pa /
NK031(ki)006:1558: pan+di ta stong gi slob dpon du gyur pa zhig bzhugs so zer nas /
NK031(ki)006:1559: khong da lta gang na bzhugs byas pas /
NK031(ki)006:1561: seng ldeng bsil byed kyi tshal /
NK031(ki)006:1563: rin po che za ma tog spung pa'i khab na bzhugs zer te /
NK031(ki)006:1565: bram ze mo blo gros dri med bya ba la 'phrin bardzangasa pa /
NK031(ki)006:1566: thugs rje ma smin smon lam ma dag pas //
NK031(ki)006:1567: 'phags pa'i bzhugs gnas sems can gnas su 'gyangs //
NK031(ki)006:1568: sdug po 'thibs bsal 'phags pa'i nyi zhal khum //
NK031(ki)006:1569: thugs rjes nyi zhal ston la thugs rje'i zhags pas gzung du gsol /
NK031(ki)006:1572: 'phags pa'i 'phags pa bstod pa khyed kyi gnyer /
NK031(ki)006:1573: dkon mchog bla med rin chen mchod gnas la /
NK031(ki)006:1574: basngagasa pa mthong ba tshogs rnams skye ba'i rgyu /
NK031(ki)006:1575: sems kyi rgyus pas yan lag thang bcad ces /
NK031(ki)006:1576: dka' bas byon pas bdag kyang dga' ba'i mchog /
NK031(ki)006:1577: shes rgyud sbyangs nas khad kyis mjal bar bagyi'o //
NK031(ki)006:1581: phyag dang bskor ba byas nas zhus pa /
NK031(ki)006:1582: ma skyes spros med bde chen rang gi sems /
NK031(ki)006:1583: rang la yod kyang rgya gar yul du thug /
NK031(ki)006:1584: bod kyi spu rgyal yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK031(ki)006:1585: gu ru zab mo bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos zhig zhu /
NK031(ki)006:1588: bod la bee ro tsa na bdag /
NK031(ki)006:1589: o rgyan thor cog yul du ni /
NK031(ki)006:1590: rgyal po ba la de bar skyes /
NK031(ki)006:1591: de nas kha che gri brtan du /
NK031(ki)006:1592: tsan d+ha g+hir ti zhes su grags //
NK031(ki)006:1593: ping nga yul gyi ma la ru //
NK031(ki)006:1594: dge slong legs pa'i blo gros te //
NK031(ki)006:1595: mkhan la brgal ba'i rnam smin gyis //
NK031(ki)006:1596: tsha ba'i phyug lji shed cag go //
NK031(ki)006:1597: dus der 'gyod de sdom blang bas /
NK031(ki)006:1598: phyi ma dge slong dus na'o //
NK031(ki)006:1599: de nas rgya gar yul du ni //
NK031(ki)006:1600: bram ze dpal ldan bya ba'i bu //
NK031(ki)006:1601: dge slong a ba kha 'du zhes //
NK031(ki)006:1602: thu bo ya ba 'du ti dang //
NK031(ki)006:1603: nu bo 'ba' hu ra tu grags //
NK031(ki)006:1604: da lta thu bo khri stong ste //
NK031(ki)006:1605: nu bo de gzhan legs grub bo //
NK031(ki)006:1607: mi lus lan bdun blangs kyi skal ldan khyod //
NK031(ki)006:1608: rang la rtogs pa yod kyang 'gro don spyod //
NK031(ki)006:1609: bslab tshul yin pas sgra dang tshad ma slob //
NK031(ki)006:1610: rgya gar phrag dog che bas chos ni bshad par dka' //
NK031(ki)006:1612: dang po phan pa'i dbang bcu bskur nas /
NK031(ki)006:1613: rgya gar gyi rgyal po rnams ni khrims dam /
NK031(ki)006:1614: pan+di ta rnams phrag dog che /
NK031(ki)006:1615: mkha' 'gro dang ma mo rnams gnyan /
NK031(ki)006:1616: chos skyong ba'i srungs ma rnams mi bsgrungs pas 'bras bu'i chos ni dka' /
NK031(ki)006:1617: rgyu'i chos bshad kyis gsungs nas /
NK031(ki)006:1618: dang po sgra mi mthun pa sum brgya drug cu lo brgyad du bslabs /
NK031(ki)006:1619: de nas tshad ma'i bstan bcos dang mdo sde pha rol du phyin pa lo bcur bshad nas /
NK031(ki)006:1623: phyag dang bskor ba byas nas zhus pa /
NK031(ki)006:1624: chos kyi dbyings la zad med cing //
NK031(ki)006:1625: gang zag blo la thug med pas //
NK031(ki)006:1626: mkhas pa'i yang rab bdag gi pha //
NK031(ki)006:1627: 'bras bu'i chos gcig bshad du gsol //
NK031(ki)006:1630: legs so skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK031(ki)006:1631: rgyu la 'bras bu dgos pa'i phyir //
NK031(ki)006:1632: gsang sngags rdo rje'i chos bshad gyis //
NK031(ki)006:1633: bu yi blo gros brtan par bzungs //
NK031(ki)006:1635: nus pa'i dbang lnga bskur nas /
NK031(ki)006:1637: yo ga ngan song sbyongs mdangs /
NK031(ki)006:1638: ma h+aa tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad dang /
NK031(ki)006:1639: lung gi tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad la sogs pa gsang
NK031(ki)006:1640: sngags phyi nang gi rgyud sde brgya rtsa brgyad lo
NK031(ki)006:1641: dgur bshad nas / da tshim mam gsungs pas /
NK031(ki)006:1644: phyag dang bskor ba byas nas zhus pa /
NK031(ki)006:1645: ma skyes rnam dag rdzogs pa che //
NK031(ki)006:1646: spros bral thig le nyag gcig la //
NK031(ki)006:1647: bzang ngan mtho dman mi bdog kyang //
NK031(ki)006:1648: la zlo'i chos gcig bskur te zhu //
